        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/Rocky/scene_dugong.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 26a264b6-a25a-4b17-9e4d-17dc7e2e22d8).Image",
        "Description": "The plot thickens; we have located two militant cells associated with Athena, who was the CEO of the bank that was to pay for the Romanian Job. These militants are codenamed The Davids (a smaller but better trained and more strategic militia) and The Goliaths (a much, MUCH larger terrorist group that sacrifices equipment quality and training for sheer size). were going to take out the Davids first, to reduce their strategic capabilities and allow us to get some more mission critical intelligence",
